"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the Paris Olympics, Zareen spoke to Al Jazeera about her early days in boxing, growing up in an orthodox family and her goals for the future.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999994332921929, \"rank\": 5.6670264465362e-07, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"Zareen\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"her early days\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"an orthodox family\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"her goals\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: When did you start boxing?\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nikhat Zareen:I was into athletics initially and competed in 100m and 200m events.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nikhat Zareen\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"100m\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"200m events\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While I was training one day, I noticed women in all sports except boxing and asked my father, \\\"Is boxing not for girls?\\\"\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"all sports\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told me girls are capable of boxing, but our society thinks they are not strong enough for such (combat) sports.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"our society\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"such (combat) sports\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I found that very odd because I grew up playing with boys.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father then asked me if I was sure about my decision to pick up boxing and I said yes.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My father\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"my decision\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to prove to everyone that girls are strong too.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father understood me and signed me up for coaching in 2009.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My father\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: Your father supported you.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999994332921929, \"rank\": 5.6670264465362e-07, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your father\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What about your mother?\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your mother\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zareen:My mother was fine with me competing in athletics, but when she learned I wanted to box professionally, she was a bit unhappy.\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zareen\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"My mother\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to spar with boys often and the first time I returned home after a session, I came back with a bleeding nose and bruises on my eye.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"a session\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleeding nose\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"bruises\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"my eye\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When my mom saw me in that condition, she began crying and said: \\\"This is why I did not want you to pick up boxing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mom\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"that condition\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My mother believed boxing was too physical and had concerns that if I broke bones or injured my face while sparring, I would not be able to find a groom in the future.\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My mother\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"bones\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"a groom\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I told her, \\\"Do not worry.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I make a name in boxing, there will be a queue of men waiting for me!\\\"\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a name\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"a queue\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: Did you face any cultural barriers when you started boxing?\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any cultural barriers\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zareen:I had a busy schedule while I trained in my early days, so I barely had time to meet friends or family.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zareen\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"a busy schedule\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"my early days\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But whenever my parents spoke to our extended family or neighbours, those people would often ask why my parents let me sign up for a dangerous sport like boxing.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"our extended family\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"neighbours\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"those people\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerous sport\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that time, our family wasn't financially stable, so people would warn us that we might incur more expenses if I underwent injuries.\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"our family\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3492}, {\"ngram\": \"more expenses\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But my father, being a former sportsman himself, always supported me.\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"a former sportsman\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: What are your hopes for the Paris Olympics?\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your hopes\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zareen:I have given my best in all the competitions and won a medal (several times).\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zareen\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3686}, {\"ngram\": \"all the competitions\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"several times\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will aim for the same at the Olympics, putting in 100 percent of my efforts.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3804}, {\"ngram\": \"100 percent\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"my efforts\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People want m